'''刑房'''（{{lang-en|'''Grindhouse'''}}）是一種在[[美國|美國]]會長期放映[[剝削電影|剝削電影]]的戲院。該電影策劃能能追溯至1920年代初，「Grindhouse」一詞經常被錯誤地與[[紐約市|紐約市]][[42街_(曼哈頓)|42街]]的都市娛樂等領域<ref name=Church-11>{{cite journal |author=Church, David |title=From Exhibition to Genre: The Case of Grind-House Films |journal=Cinema Journal |volume=50 |number=4 |date=Summer 2011 |url=https://www.academia.edu/6632128/From_Exhibition_to_Genre_The_Case_of_Grind-House_Films |accessdate=24 March 2017 |archive-date=2018-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511194513/http://www.academia.edu/6632128/From_Exhibition_to_Genre_The_Case_of_Grind-House_Films |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=Church, David |url=https://www.academia.edu/6632405/Grindhouse_Nostalgia_Memory_Home_Video_and_Exploitation_Film_Fandom |title=Grindhouse Nostalgia: Memory, Home Video, and Exploitation Film Fandom |location=Edinburgh |publisher=Edinburgh University Press |date=2015 |isbn= |accessdate=24 March 2017 |archive-date=2018-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511194513/http://www.academia.edu/6632405/Grindhouse_Nostalgia_Memory_Home_Video_and_Exploitation_Film_Fandom |dead-url=no }}</ref>搞混，這詞最早來自在紐約會跳色情[[脫衣舞|脫衣舞]]的戲院。該電影院含有三種標準，分別為「不斷的放映各種電影」、「入場費低」、「放映的都是些低品質的電影」。「Grindhouse」一詞首次於《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的1923年文章中<ref>{{cite magazine |url= |title=Two-a-Day Policy Failure in Canadian Grind Houses |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=6 December 1923 |magazine=Variety |page=19}}</ref>。

